title: Wholemeal Banana Muffins
ingredients: ['3 ripe bananas, mashed', '200g dark brown soft sugar', '1 egg', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '120ml vegetable oil', '240g wholemeal flour', '80g porridge oats', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1 tablespoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda']
